{"tid":2055163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開口埋口「人血饅頭」果班，唔係五毛就係賤人","createTime":"2020-06-07T17:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T18:40:14.000Z","uid":171506,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82f15d9c6279fab7571fd0ce3fe18d1e817aed94","tid":2055163,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:46:02.000Z","msg":"例子1:<br />\n<br />\n。。。蔡英文打香港牌贏咗選舉，有人係連登話蔡英文食人血饅頭。。。<br />\n<br />\n咁唔通韓國瑜贏咗先無人血饅頭食？國民黨贏咗，銅鑼灣書店早被黑幫鏟平，桐叔仲可以咁順利開舖接濟手足，仲有便衣警察長期保護咁穩陣？<br />\n<br />\n例子2：<br />\n<br />\n。。。黃店貼文宣，成行成市，又係人血饅頭？。。。<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆鏟晒，只靠個別黃店貼文宣，提醒市民抗爭未完。如果有顧客因為店黃而幫襯，店主就視為食人血饅頭，咁當初講乜撚嘢黃色經濟圈？經濟圈唔係要有錢賺先維持到？<br />\n<br />\n例子3：<br />\n<br />\n選舉（遲D實大把人講）<br />\n<br />\n結論：「人血饅頭」同「國家安全」一樣，都係意義含糊的萬能key，點屈人都得。"},{"pid":"e7ded9aab4be51b9ddb09074ccace372bb247410","tid":2055163,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb709717b8192f414d6957de61377be4310334f","tid":2055163,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33bc97190ed581d17a09614304c3b5f5561b225a","tid":2055163,"uid":205785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"講呢啲說話嘅人我諗十個有九個都冇睇過藥"},{"pid":"d8bc899004fb9fbd62972ce77f61f1da9b49d581","tid":2055163,"uid":347944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T18:03:27.000Z","msg":"一係cls"},{"pid":"87f30488737b3f7635619a52116f03fee53cd66d","tid":2